sigkdd#Hotel: The hotel is the child of the conference hall.

sigkdd#Place: The main office is the parent of the conference hall and the hotel.

sigkdd#Abstract: Abstract is a child of document which is parented by paper.

sigkdd#Document: The abstract of the document is the parent of the paper and the review document.

sigkdd#Deadline_Abstract_Submission: The deadline for abstract submission is the child of the deadline author notification.

sigkdd#Best_Applications_Paper_Award: The best applications paper award is the child of the best research paper award.

sigkdd#Award: The award is the parent of the best applications paper award, the best student paper award and the best research paper award.

sigkdd#Deadline_Paper_Submission: The deadline for paper submission is the child of the deadline and the parent of the deadline author notification.

sigkdd#Deadline: The deadline for abstract submission and paper submission is the parent of the deadline author notification.

sigkdd#Deadline_Author_notification: The deadline author notification is child of the deadline and the parent of the deadline abstract submission.

sigkdd#Webmaster: The webmaster is a child of the organization which is parented by a member of the program committee.

sigkdd#Organizator: The parent organization is the organizing committee member, the program chair and the webmaster. The speaker is the parent of the author of paper student and the speaker is the parent of the speaker.

sigkdd#Author_of_paper_student: The author of paper student is the child of a speaker who is a child of a person who is a child of a Thing.

sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Award: The best student paper award is the child of the award and the parent of the best research paper award.

sigkdd#Author: The author of paper is the parent of the author of paper student. The author is also the child of a speaker and a child of a Thing.

sigkdd#ACM_SIGKDD: acm sigkdd is a child of Thing.

sigkdd#Sponzor: The sponsor of the best student paper is the sponsor of the exhibitors and is the parent of the platinum and silver supporters.

sigkdd#Exhibitor: The best student paper supporter is the parent of the exhibitors who are the child of the sponsor.

sigkdd#Registration_SIGMOD_Member: The registration fee for sigkdd members is the child of the registration fee.

sigkdd#Registration_fee: The registration fee is for the sigkdd member, the registered student and the registered non member. The parent of the student is the registration student and the child is the sponsor.

sigkdd#Person: The speaker is the parent of the invited speaker and the listener. The organization is the parent of the program committee member and the child of Thing.

sigkdd#Bronze_Supporter: The bronze supporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the gold supporter.

sigkdd#Committee: The committee is the parent of the program committee, the organizing committee and the best paper awards committee.

sigkdd#Platinum_Supporter: The platinum supporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the bronze supporter.

sigkdd#Conference_hall: The conference hall is the child of the hotel.

sigkdd#Best_Paper_Awards_Committee: The best paper awards committee is the child of the committee and the parent of the program committee.

sigkdd#Program_Chair: The program chair is a child of an organization which is parented by a speaker.

sigkdd#Main_office: The main office is the child of the conference hall.

sigkdd#Registration_Non-Member: The registered non member is the child of the registration fee and the parent of the registered sigkdd member.

sigkdd#Fee: The registration fee is the parent of the registration non member and the sponsor fee.

sigkdd#Review: Review is a child of document which is parented by paper.

sigkdd#Sponzor_fee: The sponsor fee is the child of the fee and the parent of the registration fee.

sigkdd#Registration_SIGKDD_Member: The registration fee for sigkdd members is child of the registration fee and the parent of the sponsor fee.

sigkdd#Program_Committee: The program committee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the organizing committee.

sigkdd#General_Chair: The general chair is a child of an organization which is a child of a person who is a child of a Thing.

sigkdd#Speaker: The speaker is the parent of the invited speaker and the author of paper. He is also the parent of the program chair and the speaker is a child of the organization.

sigkdd#Gold_Supporter: The gold supporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the silver supporter.

sigkdd#Registration_Student: The registration student is the child of the registration fee and the parent of the sponsor fee.

sigkdd#Organizing_Committee: The best paper awards committee is the parent of the committee which is the organizing committee.

sigkdd#Listener: The child of a listener is a child of a Thing.

sigkdd#Program_Committee_member: The program committee member is a child of the organization which is parented by the general chair.

sigkdd#Invited_Speaker: The invited speaker is the child of the speaker and the parent of the author of paper student.

sigkdd#Best_Research_Paper_Award: The best research paper award is the child of the award and the parent of the best student paper award.

sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Supporter: The best student paper supporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the platinum supporter.

sigkdd#Paper: The paper is the child of the document which is the parent of the review.

sigkdd#Silver_Supporter: The silver supporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the best student paper supporter.

sigkdd#Organizing_Committee_member: The organizing committee member is a child of an organization which is a child of a person who is a child of a Thing.

sigkdd#Author_of_paper: The author of the paper is the child of the author and the speaker. The speaker is the parent of the invited speaker.
